question: Musk vs. Zuck
description:
This market will resolve to "Musk" if Elon Musk wins any scheduled fight between himself and Mark Zuckerberg within this market's timeframe. This market will resolve to "Zuck" if Mark Zuckerberg wins any scheduled fight between himself and Elon Musk within this market's timeframe.

If such a fight is considered a draw, is cancelled, or is otherwise comes to an end without a definitive winner, this market will resolve 50-50.

If no fight between Elon Musk and Mark Zuckerberg is scheduled by April 1, 2024, 11:59 PM ET, this market will resolve 50-50.

If a fight between Elon Musk and Mark Zuckerberg is scheduled before April 1, 2024, 11:59 PM ET but is set to take place after that date, the timeframe of this market will extend until that fight's set date. If that fight's date is postponed to a point within 60 days of the original set date, this market's timeframe will extend to the new fight date. If that fight's date is postponed to a point over 60 days after its original set date, this market will resolve 50-50.

question: Musk vs. Zuck: Will the richer man win?
description:

question: Haaland to break PL goal record this season?
description:
The Premier League's 2023/24 season will start on August 11, 2023, and the final match round is scheduled for May 19, 2024.

This market will resolve to "Yes" if Erling Haaland scores 37 or more goals in the Premier League's 2023/24 season. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

This market will resolve as soon as Erling Haaland scores his 37th goal in the Premier League 2023/24 season, or otherwise plays his last scheduled match in the Premier League 2023/24 season.

The resolution source for this market will be official information from the Premier League (e.g. https://www.premierleague.com/players/65970/Erling-Haaland/stats?co=1&se=489).
